==English==

==={{acronym}}=== 
'''RBI'''

#{{baseball}} The baseball statistic of "Runs Batted In" that records the number of runs that a given player has caused to be scored by either a hit, walk, or sacrafice in the course of a game, a season, a career, against this pitcher, etc.

